            <p class="card-text">
                My name is Herman Samra and I am a Junior Software Developer. I have recently completed my BSc. In Computer Science at the University of British Columbia (May 2019). During my time there, I took coursework in databases, artificial intelligence, machine learning, and computer vision. Outside of classes, I served as a Councillor for the Science Undergraduate Society and was elected by my peers to be the student representative for the department of Computer Science.
            </p>
