            <p class="card-text">
                After getting the opportunity to work with ASP .Net Core 2.1 during an internship, I was inspired to extend what I learned and to create a fully functional application using MVC. Thanks to the power of .Net Core, I was able to produce the back end (C#), front end (html), and database (SQL) for this project with this single framework alone. This blog also utilizes Trumbowyg, a light weight WYSISYG text editor written in JavaScript. Through Facebook integration, each of the blog posts feature a dedicated comment section, and one click sharing.
                Check out more details by visiting my <a href="https://github.com/h-samra/Personal-Blog">GitHub repository</a> for this project.
            </p>
